name: deceq12i
params: class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3

stmt.origin: eqtri(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3), cdc(c2, c1))
stmt.pretty: eqtri(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3), cdc(c2, c1))

body.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
-| wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c1))
-| wceq(cdc(c2, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
body.pretty:
⊢ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c1)
⊣ cdc(c2, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)

cumulated.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
-| wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c1))
-| wceq(cdc(c2, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
cumulated.pretty:
⊢ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c1)
⊣ cdc(c2, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)

body.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c1))
-| wceq(c0, c2)
body.pretty:
⊢ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c1)
⊣ c0 = c2

cumulated.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
-| wceq(cdc(c2, c1), cdc(c2, c3))

cumulated.pretty:
⊢ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ cdc(c2, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ c0 = c2

body.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c2, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
-| wceq(c1, c3)
body.pretty:
⊢ cdc(c2, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ c1 = c3

cumulated.origin:
|- wceq(cdc(c0, c1), cdc(c2, c3))
-| wceq(c0, c2)
-| wceq(c1, c3)

⊢ cdc(c0, c1)= cdc(c2, c3)
⊣ c0 = c2
⊣ c1 = c3
